3765225\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012190/extras/2fbccf5f588dfa011f654ff5546c5fc9.webm?t=1773765225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012190/extras/2fbccf5f588dfa011f654ff5546c5fc9.mp4?t=1773765225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your city-state rises from the ashes of the Great War, you’ll encounter other emerging city-states, each vying for power. Will you forge alliances or seize dominance through open conflict with your rivals? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With 100 different regions to conquer, choose your strategies and harness your resources to wage war across land, sea, and air—expanding the influence of your great empire. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012190/extras/853b53993035abb34e67527114002e30.poster.avif?t=1773765225\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012190/extras/853b53993035abb34e67527114002e30.webm?t=1773765225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012190/extras/853b53993035abb34e67527114002e30.mp4?t=1773765225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
